c', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/28330/', '', 'Dexfenfluramine, Ephedrine, Fenfluramine, Phentermine, Orlistat, Lorcaserin, Sibutramine, Diethylpropion, Mazindol, Citalopram, Sertraline, More', '', 1767369485);
